    "body": "Those tricks allow things like this \r\n```\r\n> $z = $y = $x = 1  # Sets all 3 to 1 \r\n\r\n> $z += $y += ++ $x  # Makes x 2, adds it y, and then adds Y to Z\r\n\r\n> $x,$y,$z\r\n\r\n2\r\n3\r\n4\r\n```",
